Steps:
[AUTH] obtain admin Bearer token via POST {{BACK_URL}}/connect/token
[HTTP] PUT {{BACK_URL}}/api/loyalty-setting with body: {storeId: @td(STORE_PRIMARY.id); loyaltyEnabled: true; loyaltyMode: 'Loyalty Store'; loyaltyCurrency: @td(LOYALTY_SETTINGS.currency_code)}
[HTTP] GET {{BACK_URL}}/api/loyalty-setting/store/@td(STORE_PRIMARY.id)
